s, and more than 200 items to interact with. The game is designed for room scale and features a teleporting system.\n\n- In case you get stuck, a built-in hint system provides you with clues. You\u2019ll also get in-game statistics about your performance, and there are achievements to unlock!\n\nWill you take on the challenge? Will you manage to escape the basement?", "short_description": "You find yourself locked in the cell of an unknown basement with nothing else than a bed and a toilet. Can you escape? Explore the environment, solve puzzles, investigate clues, and find your way through a total of 7 rooms to -hopefully- escape the basement of this VR escape room game."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.escapevr.net/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Five Mind Creations UG (haftungsbeschr\u00e4nkt)", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.escapevr.net/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "394813081514456"}, {"id": "377978390272490"}, {"id": "275629210202852"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "de", "ru", "zh_CN", "zh_TW", "zh_HK", "en_US", "en_AU", "en_CA", "en_ZA", "en_GB"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8223548827681853"}, "review_messages": ["", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031631_1018270826663949_8591304550852009577_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc